org.anarres.jdiagnostics

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.anarres.jdiagnostics.Result

  • public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
    A result. Results are usually sorted by key (using TreeMap). To preserve order of addition, call new Result(new LinkedHashMap()). In a query, override AbstractQuery.newResult().
